data.description: COME STEP INTO THIS COZY, CABIN STYLE HOME, WITH 3 BEDROOMS AND 2 UPDATED BATHROOMS. THIS HOME BOASTS A CHARMING FARMHOUSE RENOVATED KITCHEN. THERE IS A BEAUTIFUL BRICK WALL THAT SEPARATES THE LIVING ROOM FROM THE DINING AREA. THERE A FIRE PIT AND STORAGE SHED IN THE SPACIOUS BACKYARD, ALONG WITH ENCLOSED BACK PORCH WHICH IS PERFECT FOR A GREENHOUSE, ETC. VINYL FLOORING IN KITCHEN AND MASTER BEDROOM. ENGINEERED HARDWOOD FLOORING THROUGHOUT THE REST OF THIS HOME. CONVENIENTLY LOCATED MINUTES FROM TURNPIKE AND SHOPPING. AIR CONDITIONER NEW IN 2021.
